{"tid":2249034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泰國準備大幅度控制媒體","createTime":"2020-10-19T05:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T02:26:27.000Z","uid":310867,"like":521,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"744fada0e020d68eb18d63ec14275c5d78e372cc","tid":2249034,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T05:11:04.000Z","msg":"政府準備要控制四個媒體<br />\n<br />\nVoice TV<br />\nThe Reporters<br />\nTHE STANDARD<br />\nประชาไท <a href=\"http://Prachatai.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FPrachatai.com&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zm5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=795e1fe2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Prachatai.com</a><br />\n<br />\n這四個媒體是每天都會去現場直播給我們看狀況。<br />\n<br />\n還有準備抓討論抗議活動，或參加活動拍照等等的 300,000 個URL，意思就是準備抓三十萬人。<br />\n<br />\n這個部門就是之前要告臉書，如果臉書不封鎖討論皇室的群組，不是真的去告臉書，而是告泰國臉書公司的員工。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">有抗議就暴力解散，然後從一個地點變全泰國，從一組人變一國人。<br />\n抗議有領導人就抓領導人，然後大家都變領導人。<br />\n討論皇室的群組經營很久才有一定的人數被封閉了，隔天就有百萬人加入<br />\n媒體有報導就要封閉媒體，然後大家就會變媒體。</span><br />\n<br />\n學不會就是學不會。<br />\n<br />\n百萬人都出來了，泰國史上最大的一次抗議了。<br />\n<br />\n#saveสื่อเสรี<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰華眼裡的泰國Taihua Lin ：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/169194527226035/posts/817542572391224/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F169194527226035%2Fposts%2F817542572391224%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9Zm5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=73b1b385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/169194527226035/posts/817542572391224/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a><br />\n可以follow下，平時有news同泰文教學<br />\n<br />\n極權行為會繼續升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c3032f6de7794e6046f17aba30e59e21e999f8","tid":2249034,"uid":183758,"like":136,"dislike":5,"score":131,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T05:13:23.000Z","msg":"肯定背後有支共手影"},{"pid":"86be84cd3dad75a61f052a8fe5a47ec061dce99e","tid":2249034,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime